The paper proposes a method to learn a convolutional neural network (CNN) model to maximize the Pos@Top performance measure in machine learning problems. This involves using a classifier function to predict labels from the CNN representation of multi-instance data points. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval)
